724229f-a.title: Manhattan: Water Street - Broad Street
724229f-a.text:
Water Street, west side, north from Broad Street, to and including
Coenties Slip. Also shown is Broad Street, at and adjoining the N.W.
corner of Water Street. (Direction of Water Street, is arhitrarily set
to run North and South.)
March 26, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
